f soil profile locations. However, as the SoilGrids system is highly automated and flexible, increasingly accurate predictions can be generated as new input data become available. SoilGrids1km are available for download via http://soilgrids.org under a Creative Commons Non Commercial license.},
author = {Hengl, Tomislav and de Jesus, Jorge Mendes and MacMillan, Robert a and Batjes, Niels H and Heuvelink, Gerard B M and Ribeiro, Eloi and Samuel-Rosa, Alessandro and Kempen, Bas and Leenaars, Johan G B and Walsh, Markus G and Gonzalez, Maria Ruiperez},
